---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Passion — Jinit Shah"
  description="What Jinit Shah cares about: Handsway (real-time ASL translation), the AI & ML Club at Virginia Tech, mentoring, and volunteering."
  current="/passion"
  headerOn="light"
>
  <section class="section theme-light-bold quote-hero centered">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <h2>“Unless someone like you cares a whole awful lot, nothing is going to get better. It’s not.”</h2>
      <p>— Dr. Seuss</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3><strong>Handsway</strong></h3>
        <p><strong>Founder</strong> <em>(Feb 2022 - Present)</em></p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/handsway/id1641972653" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Handsway App Link</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Won Kickstart VT</strong> hosted by Apex Center for Entrepreneurs - Virginia
            Tech, and received seed funding and became a part of Startup Hokies Incubator program.
          </li>
          <li>
            Handsway is a one-of-a-kind, completely free, mobile application that uses machine
            learning to translate ASL signs to text using your phone camera in real time.
          </li>
          <li>
            Solely gathered the dataset, made the Machine learning model and incorporated it into
            an iOS application
          </li>
          <li>
            Handsway has won <strong>$4K+ in funding</strong> and helped <strong>2k+ users</strong>.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3><strong>AI &amp; ML Club at VT</strong></h3>
        <p><strong>President</strong> <em>(Spring 2021 - Fall 2023)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>My team and I managed and grew the club from 20 to 500+ members.</li>
          <li>Gave lectures on various ML models with hands-on coding tutorials to my fellow club members.</li>
          <li>Hosted AWS Deep Racer Competition with Peraton.</li>
          <li>
            Collaboratively worked on innovative ML projects and invited industry leading
            professionals to share their experiences and guide us.
          </li>
          <li class="tech-list">
            ML - Python - Jupyter - Numpy - Keras - Matplotlib - TensorFlow - Anaconda - SciPy -
            OpenCV
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>DSPM Program</h3>
        <p><strong>Mentor</strong> <em>(Spring 2022 &amp; Fall 2022)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Mentor for Diversifying Science Peer Mentoring Program started by College of Science at
            Virginia Tech.
          </li>
          <li>
            Assisted 4 mentees with academic planning and uplifting their overall college
            experience by providing them different opportunities and solution to their problems.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Neural Network and Deep Learning</h3>
        <p>Coursera Course by Andrew Ng</p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Certification Credential ID: SX68G6SK9UJ4</li>
          <li>
            Improved my Machine Learning skills and found my passion for AI after realizing its
            power to help people and solve real world problems
          </li>
          <li>Used knowledge gained to get Machine Learning skill certified by LinkedIn</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3><strong>Council of International Student Organizations</strong></h3>
        <p><strong>PR Officer</strong> <em>(Fall 2020 - Spring 2022)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>My team and I managed and exponentially grew the club to 500+ members.</li>
          <li>Gave lectures on various ML models with hands-on coding tutorials to my fellow club members.</li>
          <li>Re-registered the club, created and grew clubs Instagram, Discord &amp; YouTube</li>
          <li>
            Collaboratively worked on innovative ML projects and invited industry leading
            professionals to share their experiences and guide us.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Vawter Hall</h3>
        <p><strong>President</strong> <em>(August 2019 - June 2020)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Elected as President of my on-campus dorm at Virginia Tech.</li>
          <li>Helped improve student life and experience at my dorm</li>
          <li>Worked with Residence Hall Federation(RHF) at VT to make positive campus wide changes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-black-bold">
    <div class="section__inner split">
      <div class="entry-head">
        <h3>Oxfam at VT</h3>
        <p><strong>Outreach Coordinator</strong> <em>(August 2019 - Present)</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="entry-body">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Collaborated with local Blacksburg food banks, restaurants and farms to organize food
            drives and help the needy.
          </li>
          <li>Provided plenty food bank with on field help at their farm and kitchen.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section theme-white volunteer centered">
    <div class="section__inner">
      <h2>Volunteer!</h2>
      <p>
        Volunteering is something that is very close to my heart. I’ve been regularly volunteering
        since I was 10, however, I’ve been doing it for myself and hence I’m not going to showcase
        most of it here. The reason why I included this is because if you have any hands on
        volunteer opportunities, then feel free to reach out. I’ll be more than happy to help!
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
